Where you lived did all the people in the working class - I think you said that they didn't have the same standard of living - like the family who lived opposite you had a higher sta
ndard of living so there'd be different groups within the working class - do you think that one group felt itself superior to the rest if it had more money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14885385 DM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13590813\charrsid161096 I don't think they personally felt that you know.
