No, but when he was ill - he went - he laid in some time before he died. There was no - no money coming in and - we had to relay on what you call the relief.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4657134 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13590813\charrsid161096 Was he ever ill earlier in his life?
