Well only for a - only for a - one or two days sort of business. He was - he was comparatively fairly healthy man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4657134 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13590813\charrsid161096 So he didn't have long periods when he was ill?
