\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14885385 DM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13590813\charrsid161096 
No, only when illness was in the family. When dad's money stopped you see. Or perhaps we had a lot - a lot of w
et weather when - immediately it started raining them days they used to blow the whistle and that was the finish of the days work. Come the weekend there was no money much. Today - don't get that today. Yes.
\par 
